
= Quick reference =

== To install canoo and run the tests ==
 1. Download Canoo (http://webtest.canoo.com/webtest/manual/Downloads.html) and extract it into /usr/local/canoo folder
 2. Follow installation instruction (http://webtest.canoo.com/webtest/manual/install.html)
 3. Copy "properties/user.properties.example" to "properties/user.properties" and modify database access passwords
 4. Copy "properties/ex2.properties.example" to "properties/ex2.properties" and mofidy user access passwords
 5. Copy "lib/ant-contrib-1.0b3.jar", "lib/ant-jsch.jar" and "lib/jsch-0.1.33.jar" into both "/usr/local/ant/lib" and "/usr/local/canoo/lib" folders
    (assuming it is the location where you installed the ant and canoo)
 5. Synopsis to run all tests (from within main folder):
 {{{
 # ant test-canoo
 }}}
 
 
For full documentation on how to use and run canoo tests see wiki page:
https://developer.openads.org/wiki/CanooWebTest
